Plot:
    - Starts game as a child playing with friends with a simple ability
    - Son dies and you continue the rest of the game as Graham the father of the son
    - Grahams play style is just a more complex version of his son
    - Graham suffers a heavy loss
    - Graham is slowly devoured by pain and hate
    - Graham becomes the final boss of act one (stats stay the same)
    - Time skip to No.1 waking up after being rebooted
    - No.1 gathers the gang
    - 